<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="not-answered">Prayer area <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">On-site chapel <span>(not answered)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentcad49990820b4a9592fefafc03595451">
</div>
<p>There is a chapel at The Royal Marsden's Chelsea site as well as a separate prayer room. Both are open around the clock. The hospital chaplains, who represent many different world faiths, can be contacted through the main hospital switchboard. They will be there for you if you are a patient, visitor or member of staff, and whether or not you have a religious faith.</p>
